\\includegraphics[width=\\textwidth]{_page_0_Figure_2.jpeg}
\\caption{Multiple-clock-cycle pipeline diagram of five instructions. This style of pipeline representation shows the complete execution of instructions in a single figure. Instructions are listed in instruction execution order from top to bottom, and clock cycles move from left to right. Unlike Figure 4.26, here we show the pipeline registers between each stage. Figure 4.59 shows the traditional way to draw this diagram.}
\\label{fig:4.45}
\\end{figure}

